[Name] OpenTTD
[Summary] An Open Source clone of Transport Tycoon Deluxe
[License] GNU Public Licence, Version 2.0
[Description] OpenTTD is a clone of the Microprose game 
"Transport Tycoon Deluxe", a popular game originally written 
by Chris Sawyer. It attempts to mimic the original game as 
closely as possible while extending it with new features.

Some files from "Transport Tycoon Deluxe" are needed to
run OpenTTD. They can be obtained from the TTD CD.
[Homepage] http://www.openttd.org
